      "side": 1,
      "message": "The @singleton annotation adds nothing here. The @Component is the OSGi DS annotation. OSGi DS manages the lifecycle. The default service scope is ServiceScope.SINGLETON. The SCR reads the @Component and creates exactly one instance and hands it to every consumer. That guarantee comes entirely from @Component, not from @Singleton.",
